1050
00:58:14,375 --> 00:58:17,209
Jacob V. Manjooran from 8-C...
His sister had an accident.

1051
00:58:17,250 --> 00:58:18,459
She's in critical condition.

1052
00:58:18,500 --> 00:58:20,876
Avinash, I need you to go with him
to the hospital.

1053
00:58:20,918 --> 00:58:22,709
I'll have a staff member
go with you.

1054
00:58:22,751 --> 00:58:25,417
- Okay, Ma'am.
- Jacob's parents will be there.

1055
00:58:25,459 --> 00:58:27,167
Till then, make sure that he's fine.

1056
00:58:27,209 --> 00:58:28,209
Sure, Ma'am.

1057
00:58:35,000 --> 00:58:36,709
She's in the ICU.
Third floor.

1058
