1069
01:00:10,375 --> 01:00:12,000
and set her free...

1070
01:00:13,500 --> 01:00:16,125
they need my permission.

1071
01:00:19,125 --> 01:00:21,834
They need a... "Yes" from me.

1072
01:00:25,209 --> 01:00:26,250
But...

1073
01:00:28,292 --> 01:00:30,500
unless... unless you also say "Yes"...

1074
01:00:32,667 --> 01:00:33,959
I won't say "Yes."

1075
01:00:39,500 --> 01:00:40,959
If I say "Yes"...

1076
01:00:42,250 --> 01:00:43,834
will Chechi be happy?

1077
01:00:45,167 --> 01:00:46,167
Yes.

1078
01:00:50,042 --> 01:00:51,083
Promise?

1079
01:00:54,250 --> 01:00:55,292
Promise.

1080
