My Mummy's name is Annie.

1086
01:01:50,792 --> 01:01:52,417
Chacko's real name is Jacob.

1087
01:01:53,334 --> 01:01:55,292
Same name as my grandfather.

1088
01:01:55,334 --> 01:01:56,709
What's your name?

1089
01:01:59,209 --> 01:02:00,209
Delulu.

1090
01:02:00,834 --> 01:02:02,417
That's just the name
we gave you, right?

1091
01:02:03,459 --> 01:02:04,792
What's your real name?

1092
01:02:06,292 --> 01:02:07,459
Delulu...

1093
01:02:08,876 --> 01:02:10,209
means delusion...

1094
01:02:12,334 --> 01:02:13,375
means Maya.

1095
