"Don't disappear and fill my heart
with painful spears"

1098
01:02:56,667 --> 01:03:02,334
"Wasn't it in your eyes
that I saw myself clearer"

1099
01:03:02,375 --> 01:03:06,876
"As though I stood
before a living mirror?"

1100
01:03:07,292 --> 01:03:10,292
"When I stood all alone
in silent plea"

1101
01:03:10,334 --> 01:03:16,918
