1127
01:06:00,334 --> 01:06:01,334
Indu...

1128
01:06:01,417 --> 01:06:04,042
Everything you said
could be your imagination,

1129
01:06:04,584 --> 01:06:05,792
or it could be true.

1130
01:06:06,083 --> 01:06:09,167
I'd like to believe
that it's true.

1131
01:06:11,918 --> 01:06:15,584
Her parents haven't seen
the person she loved, till date.

1132
01:06:19,751 --> 01:06:21,959
A soul can find
peace and salvation

1133
01:06:22,500 --> 01:06:24,834
only by freeing itself
from sorrow!

1134
01:06:45,918 --> 01:06:47,292
Lakshmy, the guest room first.

1135
01:06:47,334 --> 01:06:48,375
Okay, Madam.

1136
01:06:49,209 --> 01:06:50,209
- Would this do?
- Yes.

1137
01:06:55,918 --> 01:06:56,918
Yes?

1138
01:06:57,167 --> 01:06:58,751
I'm a friend of Maya's.

1139
01:06:59,375 --> 01:07:01,167
I was in the area
and thought I'd drop by.

1140
01:07:02,334 --> 01:07:03,375
Oh.

1141
01:07:03,751 --> 01:07:04,751
Come in.

1142
01:07:12,918 --> 01:07:14,250
Maya always used to say...

1143
01:07:15,209 --> 01:07:17,083
that regardless of how much
you both fought,

1144
01:07:17,125 --> 01:07:19,083
when she was away,
the one she missed the most...

1145
01:07:20,125 --> 01:07:21,334
was her mom.

1146
01:07:21,834 --> 01:07:23,209
She's a big liar.

1147
01:07:23,250 --> 01:07:25,751
She'd say the exact same thing
about her Papa.

1148
01:07:28,500 --> 01:07:30,959
We still haven't been able
to accept that reality

1149
01:07:31,292 --> 01:07:34,167
So, we don't really...
miss her, as such.

1150
