Her Papa has turned
into a complete workaholic.

1151
01:07:40,209 --> 01:07:42,209
And Chacko keeps studying
all the time.

1152
01:07:42,250 --> 01:07:43,834
He's even the class topper now.

1153
01:07:47,667 --> 01:07:50,375
But there are two things
that really trouble me.

1154
01:07:51,125 --> 01:07:53,334
I miss her whenever I open
the fridge in the kitchen.

1155
01:07:54,292 --> 01:07:56,334
She always used to walk over
and open the fridge,

1156
01:07:56,751 --> 01:07:58,167
ever since she was a little girl.

1157
01:08:00,542 --> 01:08:03,167
And then, when I see clothes
lying all over the bed.

1158
01:08:03,792 --> 01:08:06,500
No matter how many times I told her,
she always left her clothes on the bed.

1159
01:08:07,542 --> 01:08:09,417
Clothes were her weakness.

1160
01:08:09,876 --> 01:08:12,417
She was always on her phone,
browsing for them.

1161
01:08:18,417 --> 01:08:20,083
Let me get you
something to drink.

1162
01:08:56,626 --> 01:08:58,417
"You don't like beards, Mummy."

1163
01:08:58,459 --> 01:08:59,876
"He has a beard."

1164
01:08:59,918 --> 01:09:00,918
"And..."

1165
01:09:01,417 --> 01:09:02,834
"He is a Hindu."

1166
01:09:02,876 --> 01:09:04,709
"And he's a little older than me."

1167
01:09:08,626 --> 01:09:10,083
What's your name?

1168
01:09:16,834 --> 01:09:17,834
Prabhendu.

1169
01:09:20,959 --> 01:09:23,709
You were the one she was in love with...
Isn't that right, Prabhendu?

1170
01:09:36,792 --> 01:09:37,792
Yes.

1171
01:12:20,042 --> 01:12:26,876
"When someone sat close to me at night,
like new-fallen rain in cool delight"

1172
01:12:26,918 --> 01:12:32,500
"My heart shifted, lighter than ever,
turning at once to a moonlit river"

1173
01:12:33,542 --> 01:12:37,042
"Slowly unfolding its wings
in tender delight"

1174
01:12:37,167 --> 01:12:40,584
"Weaving a chain of laughter
pure and bright"

1175
01:12:40,626 --> 01:12:46,209
"My mind fills up
on its own tonight"

1176
01:12:47,417 --> 01:12:53,042
"Come, let's go to distances
we've never seen"

1177
01:12:53,417 --> 01:12:59,417
"Becoming two lovely,
colourful clouds serene"

1178
01:12:59,459 --> 01:13:01,083
"In this new birth
where our paths convene"

1179
01:13:01,125 --> 01:13:06,876
"Let's find our shelter on a blossom
branch kissed by morning dew"

1180
01:13:06,918 --> 01:13:10,459
"Becoming the breath
that rises soft and true"

1181
01:13:10,500 --> 01:13:14,542
"Till every painful memory
softens and bids adieu"

